# Volume Control


# Light Control

Working principle.
    Usage tool 'brightnessctl' & bash script 'set_brightness.sh' for smooth lighting changes.

Setup steps.
    Install tool 'brightnessctl'.
    Copy script 'set_brightness.sh' to '~/.config/scripts/'.
    The 'hyprland.conf' file uses a script to change the lighting using hotkeys.

# Leds For MicMute & VolMute Button

Working principle.
    Usage tool 'alsa-tools' & bash script 'leds_sync.sh' for on\off lights

Setup steps.
    Install tool 'alsa-tools'.
    Copy script 'leds_sync.sh' to '~/.config/scripts/'.
    Added 'leds_sync.sh' script to background process.


